  "page": "Grazdan the Great",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For others with the same name, see <a href=\"/index.php/Grazdan_(disambiguation)\" title=\"Grazdan (disambiguation)\">Grazdan (disambiguation)</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Old_Ghis\" title=\"Old Ghis\"><img alt=\"GhisHarpie.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d4/GhisHarpie.png/50px-GhisHarpie.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d4/GhisHarpie.png/75px-GhisHarpie.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d4/GhisHarpie.png/100px-GhisHarpie.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Grazdan<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> the Great</span></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Old_Ghis\" title=\"Old Ghis\"><img alt=\"GhisHarpie.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d4/GhisHarpie.png/50px-GhisHarpie.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d4/GhisHarpie.png/75px-GhisHarpie.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d4/GhisHarpie.png/100px-GhisHarpie.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Ghiscari\" title=\"Ghiscari\">Ghiscari</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Grazdan the Great</b> is the legendary founder of <a href=\"/index.php/Old_Ghis\" title=\"Old Ghis\">Old Ghis</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Grazdan_the_Great&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>According to legend, Grazdan founded the <a href=\"/index.php/Lockstep_legions\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lockstep legions\">lockstep legions</a>, with which Old Ghis colonized its surroundings and subjugated its neighbors, forming the <a href=\"/index.php/Old_Empire_of_Ghis\" title=\"Old Empire of Ghis\">first empire</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf25.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf25.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Grazdan is also credited with raising the ancient brick walls of Old Ghis.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf25.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf25.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Legacy\">Legacy</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Grazdan_the_Great&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Legacy\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Grazdan is still so revered that men of the slaver families of <a href=\"/index.php/Slaver%27s_Bay\" title=\"Slaver&#39;s Bay\">Slaver's Bay</a> are often given his name.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf25.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf25.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Grazdan_the_Great&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf25.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf25.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf25.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf25.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Ancient History&#58; The Rise of Valyria.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_27\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 27\">Chapter 27</a>, Daenerys III.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403121423\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.079 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.294 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 664/1000000\nPre